User --> Teacher
User --> Student
User --> Center

User --> RefreshToken
User --> Follower
User --> Review

Teacher --> Course
Teacher --> Lesson

Course --> Lesson
Course --> Exam
Course --> Homework
Course --> Note

Student --> BookedLesson
Lesson --> BookedLesson

Center --> WeeklySchedule
WeeklySchedule --> TeacherDay
Teacher --> TeacherDay

Student --> BookedWeekly
TeacherDay --> BookedWeekly

User --> Post
Post --> Comment
Post --> Like
User --> Comment
